{"tid":1009938,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖人妻拿平底鍋爆打出軌夫　割下生殖器煮成「奶油雞麵」","createTime":"2019-02-05T14:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T17:32:15.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0021eac1a47ca5e98502c8007abf2ce588cdff4f","tid":1009938,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:18:00.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n奈及利亞日前發生一起恐怖妻殺夫事件！47歲人妻律師歐蒂碧（Udeme Otike-Odibi）因為懷疑50歲老公席姆（Sym）出軌，在盛怒之下竟拿平底鍋爆打席姆，將丈夫打昏後再拿刀狠刺腹部，活活將丈夫捅死，更恐怖的是，最後歐蒂碧割下席姆的陰莖，煮成一鍋「奶油雞麵」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3883/d3883779.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3883%2Fd3883779.jpg&h=9afda401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲席姆當場開腸破肚慘死。（圖／翻攝英國鏡報）<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，席姆過去曾有一段婚姻，3年前和第一任老婆離婚後，便和歐蒂碧結婚。不過近來歐蒂碧懷疑席姆在外偷吃。去年5月2人發生口角與衝突，歐蒂碧氣得衝進廚房拿起平底鍋，朝席姆頭部狠狠爆打，不斷追問「你有什麼事瞞著我嗎？」隨後更持菜刀刺向席姆腹部，導致席姆當場開腸破肚慘死。<br />\n歐蒂碧即使已將丈夫刺死仍怒氣未消，認為一切都是「小頭」在作怪，於是割下席姆的陰莖，煮成一鍋「奶油雞麵」作為報復。事後歐蒂碧還打電話告知婆婆說，「媽對不起，我們發生衝突了。」另也向朋友說，自己做了一件很恐怖的事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3883/d3883778.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3883%2Fd3883778.jpg&h=5657a49f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲丈夫下體被煮成一道「奶油雞麵」。（圖／翻攝英國鏡報）<br />\n據了解，歐蒂碧擁有奈及利亞和英國雙重國籍，案發後企圖逃到英國，不過在出境前遭到警方逮捕，並在家中找到犯案用平底鍋及刀子。歐蒂碧否認一切指控，該案將在本月25日開庭審理。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190205/1373426.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190205%2F1373426.htm&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFvroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=347d336e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190205/1373426.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ac585d1f5970c1cbc62b96701523614f3306a432","tid":1009938,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"求無格圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456301d664e53d5e8d6189d3950ea17851447960","tid":1009938,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ebbe3098cf1566114e7234701417369a9e9caa5","tid":1009938,"uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/ConfusedTalkativeAntarcticgiantpetrel-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FConfusedTalkativeAntarcticgiantpetrel-size_restricted.gif&h=4dd52edc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"158f4a8b9d9e58ba3d3f0906d19626346d71f19a","tid":1009938,"uid":188310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"條JER夠粗　可惜短過鳩毛<br />\n春袋萎縮　自瀆生涯從此結束<br />\n咁就要切柒煲粥　煲粥　煲粥嚟餵狗"},{"pid":"997552642f14153e47e591d31e2a2aa16e45eab0","tid":1009938,"uid":61882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ac585d1f5970c1cbc62b96701523614f3306a432","tid":1009938,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"求無格圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T15:05:14.000Z","msg":"之前有個一模一樣既po<br />\n就係因為個樓豬po咗無碼圖<br />\n畀連<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鏟咗po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8466039ddcfefe2e573777ab92c1dd45cf2fee33","tid":1009938,"uid":24024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T17:32:15.000Z","msg":"個麵似好食。。。"}]}